These are the COSMA specific version of the ci/ scripts. They establish the
module environment and then source the generic test scripts. When setting up
the modules it is assumed that the run is in a minimal container with access to
the /cosma/local file system this means we need to initial the module command
itself as well using:

   source /cosma/local/Modules/default/init/bash

which is normally done when a user logs in.
